1
00:00:05,633 --> 00:00:06,225
What's that...?

2
00:00:07,604 --> 00:00:12,431
Rerir? S—So the rumors about your work are true...

3
00:00:12,431 --> 00:00:15,236
What? No! Listen

4
00:00:15,236 --> 00:00:18,058
Something happened at the palace tonight, we have to leave!

5
00:00:19,875 --> 00:00:23,041
You don't need to lie to me anymore

6
00:00:23,456 --> 00:00:24,206
What do you mean?

7
00:00:25,596 --> 00:00:27,182
I know why you're worried

8
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:30,229
And I will respect the decision you've made

9
00:00:31,334 --> 00:00:36,198
But it's okay, because... I've found a solution

10
00:00:37,225 --> 00:00:39,470
I know how to end all this

11
00:00:40,058 --> 00:00:44,504
You can have it back... the normal life you so desire

12
00:00:46,096 --> 00:00:47,218
But until then...

13
00:00:48,222 --> 00:00:51,411
I'm afraid our wedding... will have to wait

14
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:57,206
Tholindis? No, don't do it!

15
00:00:57,987 --> 00:01:00,455
Tholindis!? Tholindis!!!

16
00:01:07,826 --> 00:01:15,132
I told you, Rerir, let her go. You will find someone better

17
00:01:16,059 --> 00:01:19,740
No! No, I... I won't do it! I have to save her!

18
00:01:20,660 --> 00:01:23,498
By what means, exactly?

19
00:01:23,813 --> 00:01:30,998
A lowly pawn, you lack the power and the strength of will...

20
00:01:31,671 --> 00:01:35,227
Do... Do you know a way? Tell me!

21
00:01:35,962 --> 00:01:40,461
Come to the palace. Join us

22
00:01:48,495 --> 00:01:50,649
Rerir? Thank goodness, we—

23
00:01:50,939 --> 00:01:54,883
Step forth, and take your share

24
00:01:57,414 --> 00:01:58,379
You made it

25
00:02:00,778 --> 00:02:02,141
Not you, too...

26
00:02:06,829 --> 00:02:11,806
Hatred or grief, despair or desire...

27
00:02:12,653 --> 00:02:16,071
We all have our reasons

28
00:02:26,973 --> 00:02:29,565
Rerir, Rerir!

29
00:02:30,905 --> 00:02:31,933
Tholindis...

30
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:34,629
Were you daydreaming?

31
00:02:40,067 --> 00:02:45,547
You still remember, Rerir? That question you asked me a couple of weeks ago?

32
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:50,521
Oh... you mean, the proposal?

33
00:02:51,026 --> 00:02:56,857
Yeah. I'm wondering, where do you think would be a good place to discuss it?

34
00:02:57,746 --> 00:03:01,647
Maybe in the garden? Or were you thinking a fancy restaurant?

35
00:03:04,004 --> 00:03:05,181
It's your choice

36
00:03:54,458 --> 00:03:55,699
I will find you

37
00:03:56,993 --> 00:04:00,611
And then, you can give me your answer

